HAI 1.4
    HOW IZ I fibonacci YR n
        BOTH SAEM n AN 0, O RLY?
            YA RLY, FOUND YR 0
        OIC
        BOTH SAEM n AN 1, O RLY?
            YA RLY, FOUND YR 1
        OIC
        I HAS A a ITZ 0
        I HAS A b ITZ 1
        I HAS A i ITZ 2
        IM IN YR loop UPPIN YR i TIL BOTH SAEM i AN SUM OF n AN 1
            I HAS A temp ITZ SUM OF a AN b
            a R b
            b R temp
        IM OUTTA YR loop
        FOUND YR b
    IF U SAY SO

    I HAS A i ITZ 0
    IM IN YR printloop UPPIN YR i TIL BOTH SAEM i AN 20
        VISIBLE I IZ fibonacci YR i MKAY
    IM OUTTA YR printloop
KTHXBYE
